name: Corulag Operative
Lore: 'Independent traders make money selling equipment to the academy at Corulag. Resentful of the Alliance pilots that disrupt their shipping lines.',
Text: 'While at a Corulag site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your trooper is on Corulag) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Corulag from Reserve Deckreshuffle.',
